pkgmetadata.longdescription:
@ghc-source-gen@ is a library for generating Haskell source code. It uses the <https://hackage.haskell.org/package/ghc ghc> library to support recent language extensions, and provides a simple, consistent interface across several major versions of GHC.
To get started, take a look at the "GHC.SourceGen" module.
For more information, please see the <https://github.com/google/ghc-source-gen README>.
